high_descs: Turn left and walk to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the spoon on the counter to the right of the kitchen sink.
Turn around and walk toward the door on the opposite wall from the kitchen sink.  Turn right at the door and walk toward the kitchen table.
Put the spoon down on the pan next to the toaster.
Pick up the pan with the spoon.
Turn right and walk toward the kitchen sink.
Put the pan with the spoon down in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon and pan in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight slightly then turn to the right and face the counter
Pick up the large spoon from the counter
Turn around and walk straight then turn right and walk to the brown kitchen table
Place the spoon in the back pan on the table
Pick up the pan with the spoon inside
Turn left and walk straight to the kitchen sink and face it
Place the pan and spoon inside the kitchen sink
anns.task_desc: Putting a pan and spoon in the kitchen sink

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the large metal spoon off of the counter.
Turn around and walk up to the wooden table on the right side of the room.
Put the large wooden spoon in the metal pan that is on the wooden table.
Pick up the metal pan with the large metal spoon in it off of the wooden table.
Turn right and walk over to the sink.
Put the metal pan with the spoon in it into the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a metal pan with a large spoon in it in the sink basin.
